      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So you're saying it's more about correcting a misreading than a legitimate debate over interpretation? I'm just trying to make sure I'm being fair to the curriculum standards. Is there any actual legal basis for the argument that due process should only be procedural, or is that just a way to avoid protecting certain rights?",
